# Google OAuth client ID for the Chrome extension.
#
# This value is NOT a secret (it is embedded in the published manifest), but dev
# and production must use SEPARATE client IDs (see docs/publication.md).
#
# Required for `bun run build` (extension/production builds): the build fails
# clearly if it is missing. For local `bun run dev` a documented non-functional
# placeholder is used when this is unset.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is git-ignored) and fill in your dev
# client ID. Do not commit `.env.local` or any real client secret/token.
VITE_GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=replace-me.apps.googleusercontent.com
